msgstr "如果您是从“入门”示例开始的，那么您应该已经完成了一个测试，其中包含正确的工具配置。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "In your build file you should see 2 test dependencies:"
