#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`quarkus-junit` is required for testing, as it provides the `@QuarkusTest` annotation that controls the testing framework.\n"
"`rest-assured` is not required but is a convenient way to test HTTP endpoints, we also provide integration that automatically\n"
"sets the correct URL so no configuration is required."
msgstr "测试需要 `使用 quarkus-junit，` 因为它提供了用于控制测试框架的 `@QuarkusTest` 注解。 `rest-assured` 并非必需，但它是测试 HTTP 端点的便捷方式；此外，我们还提供了集成功能，可自动设置正确的 URL，因此无需进行任何配置。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Because we are using JUnit, the version of the https://maven.apache.org/surefire/maven-surefire-plugin/[Surefire Maven Plugin]\n"
"must be set, as the default version does not support JUnit:"
msgstr "由于我们使用的是 JUnit，因此必须设置 link:https://maven.apache.org/surefire/maven-surefire-plugin/[Surefire Maven 插件的] 版本，因为默认版本不支持 JUnit："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"We also set the `java.util.logging.manager` system property to make sure tests will use the correct logmanager and `maven.home` to ensure that custom configuration\n"
"from `${maven.home}/conf/settings.xml` is applied (if any)."
msgstr "我们还设置了 `java.util.logging.manager` 系统属性，以确保测试使用正确的日志管理器，并设置了 `maven.home` 属性，以确保应用 `${maven.home}/conf/settings.xml` 中的自定义配置（如有）。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The project should also contain a simple test:"
msgstr "该项目还应包含一个简单的测试："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This test uses HTTP to directly test our REST endpoint. When the test is run the application will be started before\n"
"the test is run."
msgstr "该测试使用 HTTP 直接测试我们的 REST 端点。运行测试时，系统会在执行测试之前先启动应用程序。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Controlling the test port"
msgstr "控制测试端口"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"While Quarkus will listen on port `8080` by default, when running tests it defaults to `8081`. This allows you to run\n"
"tests while having the application running in parallel."
msgstr "虽然 Quarkus 默认监听 `8080` 端口，但在运行测试时，默认端口会改为 `8081` 。这样，您就可以在应用程序并行运行的同时执行测试。"

#. type: Block title
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Changing the test port"
msgstr "更改测试端口"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can configure the ports used by tests by configuring `quarkus.http.test-port` for HTTP and `quarkus.http.test-ssl-port` for HTTPS in your `application.properties`:"
msgstr "您可以通过在 `application.properties` 文件中配置 `quarkus.http.test-port` （用于 HTTP）和 `quarkus.http.test-ssl-port` （用于 HTTPS）来设置测试所使用的端口："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "`0` will result in the use of a random port (assigned by the operating system)."
msgstr "`0` 将导致使用随机端口（由操作系统分配）。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus also provides RestAssured integration that updates the default port used by RestAssured before the tests are run,\n"
"so no additional configuration should be required."
msgstr "Quarkus 还提供了与 RestAssured 的集成，该集成会在运行测试前更新 RestAssured 使用的默认端口，因此无需进行额外配置。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
