#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For the purposes of these examples I am going to assume we have an endpoint that looks like the following:"
msgstr "为了便于说明，我将假设我们有一个如下所示的端点："

