msgstr "*只有在* 存在 `quarkus-junit-mockito` 依赖项 *的情况下* ， `@io.quarkus.test.InjectMock` 注解才支持此功能："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Using `@InjectMock`, the previous example could be written as follows:"
msgstr "使用 `@InjectMock` ，前面的示例可以写成如下形式："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
