msgstr "`@InjectMock` 会导致创建一个 Mockito 模拟对象，该对象随后可在测试类的测试方法中使用（其他测试类 *不受* 此影响）"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The `mockableBean1` is configured here for every test method of the class"
