msgstr "如本文档相关章节所述 `，CustomResource` 将在使用 `@QuarkusTestResource` 的 `@QuarkusIntegrationTest` 中被激活。"

#. type: Title ==
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Executing against a running application"
msgstr "在正在运行的应用程序上执行"

