#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"To alleviate this restriction, the `@QuarkusTest` annotation defines a JUnit `@Tag`: `io.quarkus.test.junit.QuarkusTest`.\n"
"You can use this tag to isolate the `@QuarkusTest` test in a specific execution run, for example with the Maven Surefire Plugin:"
msgstr "为缓解这一限制， `@QuarkusTest` 注解定义了一个 JUnit `@Tag` ： `io.quarkus.test.junit.QuarkusTest` 。您可以使用此标签在特定的执行运行中隔离 `@QuarkusTest` 测试，例如使用 Maven Surefire 插件："

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "Currently `@QuarkusTest` and `@QuarkusIntegrationTest` should not be run in the same test run."
msgstr "目前，不应在同一轮测试中同时运行 `@QuarkusTest` 和 `@QuarkusIntegrationTest` 。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For Maven, this means that the former should be run by the surefire plugin while the latter should be run by the failsafe plugin."
msgstr "对于 Maven 而言，这意味着前者应由 surefire 插件执行，而后者应由 failsafe 插件执行。"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For Gradle, this means the two types of tests should belong to different source sets."
msgstr "对于 Gradle 而言，这意味着这两类测试应属于不同的源集。"

