#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/getting-started-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can find more examples and hints in the xref:testing-components.adoc[testing components reference guide]."
msgstr "您可以在 xref:testing-components.adoc[测试组件参考指南] 中找到更多示例和提示。"
